			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Act 2 (HAV) -\r\nGo to HAV region via debug book > select \"after checkpoint\"\r\n Walk to the stables or use recon command: teleport -28 30 160\r\nThen speak to the ox in the stable furthest from the blacksmith.\r\n\r\nAct 3 (WYR) -\r\nGo to WYR region via debug book\r\nEither choose the \"refugee camp\" checkpoint or use recon command: teleport 40 51 -138 to go straight there (the ox barn is next to the big barn at the refugee camp)\r\nThen enter the ox barn and speak to the ox."
				},
