				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "This Ox is a fiendish creature in an ox's body. The ox will show the player a horrific vision from its mind, and potentially go aggro on the player if the player demands answers from it. The ox could also give a gift if the player is evil, like it."
